  "title": "Customer Service Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will serve as the first point of contact at the building’s front desk, managing administrative tasks and providing professional support to visitors and customers to ensure smooth daily operations.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage front desk administrative tasks to maintain organized and efficient operations</li><li>Answer telephone calls professionally, meeting call quality and productivity standards to support customer service</li><li>Respond to visitor and customer queries and feedback clearly and helpfully</li><li>Provide visitors with accurate information to assist their needs within the building</li><li>Assist visitors in resolving issues with turnstile access to ensure smooth entry</li><li>Represent the building positively as the first point of contact for all visitors</li><li>Perform concierge support duties as assigned by supervisors to support overall building services</li></ul>",
